statements: SELECT * FROM provider_networks;
SELECT id, provider_name FROM provider_networks WHERE network_type = 'Hospital';
SELECT provider_name, contract_start_date, contract_end_date FROM provider_networks ORDER BY contract_start_date DESC;
SELECT id, provider_name, network_type FROM provider_networks WHERE contract_end_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_providers FROM provider_networks WHERE network_type = 'Clinic';
SELECT * FROM provider_networks WHERE network_type = 'Hospital' ORDER BY provider_name DESC;
SELECT provider_name, network_type FROM provider_networks WHERE contract_start_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY provider_name ASC;
SELECT provider_name, contract_start_date, contract_end_date FROM provider_networks WHERE contract_end_date < '2023-01-01';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM provider_networks WHERE network_type = 'Clinic';
SELECT provider_name, network_type FROM provider_networks WHERE contract_start_date BETWEEN '2021-01-01' AND '2022-01-01' AND contract_end_date > '2022-08-01';
SELECT * FROM provider_networks;
SELECT network_id, network_name, location FROM provider_networks WHERE expansion_status = TRUE;
SELECT provider_id, start_date, end_date FROM contracts ORDER BY end_date DESC;
SELECT network_name, location FROM provider_networks WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT * FROM contracts WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01' AND end_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT network_id, network_name, location, expansion_status FROM provider_networks WHERE location='New York'
SELECT * FROM contracts WHERE contract_value > 5000
SELECT provider_id, start_date, end_date, contract_value FROM contracts ORDER BY start_date DESC
SELECT network_name, location FROM provider_networks WHERE expansion_status = TRUE
SELECT * FROM provider_networks WHERE network_name LIKE '%Health%'
SELECT * FROM provider_networks;
SELECT provider_name, provider_location FROM provider_networks ORDER BY provider_name ASC;
SELECT provider_name, provider_location FROM provider_networks WHERE provider_location='New York';
SELECT provider_id, provider_name FROM provider_networks ORDER BY provider_id DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_providers FROM provider_networks;
SELECT * FROM provider_networks;
SELECT provider_name, provider_location FROM provider_networks ORDER BY provider_location DESC;
SELECT provider_name, start_date FROM provider_networks JOIN contracts ON provider_networks.provider_id = contracts.provider_id;

SELECT provider_name, negotiation_date FROM provider_networks JOIN contracts ON provider_networks.provider_id = contracts.provider_id JOIN negotiations ON contracts.contract_id = negotiations.contract_id WHERE negotiation_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT provider_name, end_date FROM provider_networks JOIN contracts ON provider_networks.provider_id = contracts.provider_id WHERE end_date < '2023-01-01';
SELECT * FROM provider_network;
SELECT provider_name, network_type FROM provider_network ORDER BY provider_name DESC;
SELECT provider_name, network_size FROM provider_network WHERE network_size > 100 ORDER BY network_size ASC;
SELECT provider_name, network_type, network_size FROM provider_network WHERE provider_id BETWEEN 1 AND 5;
SELECT provider_name, network_type, network_size FROM provider_network WHERE network_type LIKE '%HMO%'
SELECT * FROM provider_network ORDER BY provider_name ASC, network_size DESC;
SELECT provider_name, network_type FROM provider_network WHERE network_size > 100 ORDER BY provider_name ASC;
SELECT provider_name, contract_value FROM provider_contract WHERE contract_start_date >= '2022-01-01' AND contract_end_date <= '2022-12-31' ORDER BY contract_value DESC;
SELECT region_name, region_description FROM network_region WHERE CHAR_LENGTH(region_description) > 50 ORDER BY region_name ASC;

SELECT pc.provider_id, pc.contract_value, nr.region_name FROM provider_contract pc JOIN network_contract_mapping ncm ON pc.contract_id = ncm.contract_id JOIN network_region nr ON ncm.region_id = nr.region_id WHERE pc.contract_value > 5000 ORDER BY pc.provider_id ASC, pc.contract_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM provider;
SELECT name, location FROM provider ORDER BY location DESC;
SELECT provider_id, network_size FROM provider WHERE network_size > 100;
SELECT * FROM contract WHERE start_date >= '2021-01-01' AND end_date <= '2021-12-31';

SELECT provider.name, network.region FROM provider JOIN network_provider ON provider.provider_id = network_provider.provider_id JOIN network ON network.network_id = network_provider.network_id WHERE network.region = 'Europe';
SELECT * FROM provider WHERE network_size > 100 ORDER BY name DESC
SELECT name, location FROM provider WHERE provider_id = 3
SELECT DISTINCT region FROM network
SELECT provider.name, negotiation.negotiation_date FROM provider JOIN negotiation ON provider.provider_id = negotiation.contract_id
SELECT provider.name, network.network_name FROM provider, network_provider, network WHERE provider.provider_id = network_provider.provider_id AND network_provider.network_id = network.network_id
